{"tid":540594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[hehe] 點樣先可以唔好再俾自己徘徊喺啲假希望","createTime":"2018-01-25T15:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T04:58:36.000Z","uid":23170,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e9d001ab988afc883dfcc55215fd1cc280fa6a","tid":540594,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"返工識左個直仔。文靜得黎但係又會周不時玩下你講下笑咁，我自己覺得佢真係好可愛。我其實唔知佢係咪真係直，之前順手攞左佢fb, 見到佢有同過女仔合照，再有聽過啲謠言佢同個女同事一齊。其實我真係明白就算佢唔係直，我都唔會係佢鍾意嘅，但係無奈依種性格嘅男仔真係好吸引，好想好想可以同佢一齊。有時佢又會搭下我膊頭或者挨得好近，我feel到佢體溫感受到佢身發出嗰股暖流，我個心又開始亂。究竟點先可以清醒到。明明識左佢加埋都只有幾日，但係已經覺得自己好難抽離，好想得到更多更多。。"},{"pid":"a150fe311fb4665e7ace74e3f286c165fb971b8f","tid":540594,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"又沉船啦你"},{"pid":"dc18ad551d7851336f071e2787451749cf755663","tid":540594,"uid":23170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a150fe311fb4665e7ace74e3f286c165fb971b8f","tid":540594,"uid":56096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"又沉船啦你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"個又字真係形容得貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明知佢鍾意女人都仲痴個頭埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢真係好可愛，尤其是佢笑嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db34685f3a472b6fffdf713e153689c1633fbac","tid":540594,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"見到佢同啲囡囡合照，好似開始清醒返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbafc319a400b0c8f295e0bdaabb1fd90bb4b30","tid":540594,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"坡仔？"},{"pid":"503f24ea05292075bb14b18e72107f1d8e35bdda","tid":540594,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bbafc319a400b0c8f295e0bdaabb1fd90bb